<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7887431>
    dc:description "Fig. 4. Habitus images of Diognetus cheimon sp.nov.(all from Nagasaki, Japan).A Ôłĺ J sucking on Eurya emarginata fruit; B Ôłĺ 5th instar nymph (left) and J on flower buds of Eurya japonica; C Ôłĺ ÔÖÇ; D Ôłĺ J (left) and ÔÖÇ sucking on young fruits of E. japonica; EÔłĺF Ôłĺ ventral habitus images ofJ (E) and ÔÖÇ (F)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation <https://zenodo.org/record/7887431/files/figure.png> ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7887433>
    dc:description "Fig. 5. Late instar immature forms and eclosion (EÔłĺH, LÔłĺM) of Diognetus cheimon sp. nov. (AÔłĺH) and D. vernus sp. nov. (IÔłĺM), observed in Nagasaki, Japan (A, JÔłĺK on Eurya japonica and BÔłĺC on E. emerginata). A Ôłĺ yellow-green form of 4th (left) and 5th instars; BÔłĺC Ôłĺ reddish form of 5th instar; D Ôłĺ 4 anal spots of 5th instar; E Ôłĺ 5th instar nymph (3 hours before eclosion, with pigmented wing-pads); FÔłĺH Ôłĺ emerging ÔÖÇ; I Ôłĺ yellow-green form of 5th instar; JÔłĺK Ôłĺ reddish form of 5th instar; LÔłĺM Ôłĺ emerging ÔÖÇ." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation <https://zenodo.org/record/7887433/files/figure.png> ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7887441>
    dc:description "Fig. 8. Male genitalia of Diognetus bagmaticus sp. nov. (AÔłĺD), D.cheimon sp. nov.(EÔłĺG), D. dhampus sp. nov. (HÔłĺJ) and D. duwalorum sp. nov.(KÔłĺM). AÔłĺB, E Ôłĺ apex of pygophore with parameres; C, H, L Ôłĺ right paramere; I, K Ôłĺ left paramere; D, FÔłĺG, J, M Ôłĺ vesica (endosoma). Scale bars 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation <https://zenodo.org/record/7887441/files/figure.png> ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7887451>
    dc:description "Fig. 10. Female genitalia of Diognetus bagmaticus sp. nov. (AÔłĺD), D. cheimon sp. nov. (EÔłĺG) and D. laureus sp. nov. (HÔłĺK). A, E Ôłĺ genital chamber; B, I Ôłĺ sclerotized ring; C, F, J Ôłĺ posterior wall; D, G, K Ôłĺ ovipositor (gonapophysis I). Scale bars 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation <https://zenodo.org/record/7887451/files/figure.png> ;
    a fabio:Figure .

